        "generic_message_normal": "Thanks for your order.\nWe are here to make your life easier, so here are some ways we can help you further...\n\u2022 EASY GIFTING: delivered FREE next business day\n\u2022 EASY FUNDRAISING: got a school / club / charity you need to raise funds for?\n\u2022 EASY CATERING: from our Nedlands store\n\nEnjoy your meals, and make life a little easier with some quick wins in the kitchen by cooking all our products straight from frozen!!\n\nNathan & the team from Tommy Sugo",
